<topic id="agent_installpackage_yum" xml:lang="en-us">
  <title>rpm Package</title>
  <shortdesc>Installation with the rpm package</shortdesc>
  <body>
    <p>The RPM-Packages are mainained by  Remi Collet.
</p>
    <p>For this, you have to install the EPEL-Repositories (<xref href="http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/EPEL" format="html">http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/EPEL</xref>) and also the Remi repository (<xref href="http://blog.famillecollet.com/pages/Config" format="html">http://blog.famillecollet.com/pages/Config</xref>)


</p>
    <p>To install the FusionInventory agent execute the following command: </p>
    <p><codeblock>yum --enablerepo=remi install fusioninventory-agent</codeblock>

</p>
    <p><note type="important">Don&apos;t use the perl packages from RPMforge.</note></p>
  </body>
